sequenceDiagram
    participant Docs as Markdown Files
    participant KB as KnowledgeBase
    participant Model as SentenceTransformer
    participant Chroma as ChromaDB

    KB->>Docs: glob("**/*.md")
    Docs-->>KB: List of files
    loop For each file
        KB->>Docs: Read content
        Docs-->>KB: File content
        KB->>KB: Split into chunks
    end
    KB->>Model: encode(documents)
    Model-->>KB: embeddings
    KB->>Chroma: upsert(documents, embeddings, metadata)
    Chroma-->>KB: Success/Fail
